<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFB06A08FA949B181AE1BA96" lastPageId="76" lastPageNumber="834" pageId="75" pageNumber="833" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFB06A08FA949B181AE1BA96" blockId="75.[1382,2590,3314,3471]" lastBlockId="76.[786,1379,269,695]" lastPageId="76" lastPageNumber="834" pageId="75" pageNumber="833">
Form hwmeralis has been treated as a species and a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFB06A0FF6F79B181788B650" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1901" box="[2315,2440,3393,3426]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glauconycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="833" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="beatrix">G. beatrix</taxonomicName>
. Here it is treated as distinct from 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFB06A0FF9499B31192EB6BB" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1901" box="[1717,1838,3432,3465]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glauconycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="833" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="beatrix">G. beatrix</taxonomicName>
, pending revision ofits taxonomic status. A. Hassanin and colleagues in 2018 retrieved 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFB76A08FB1A97541D40BA67" authorityName="J. A. Allen" authorityYear="1917" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glauconycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="76" pageNumber="834" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="humeralis">G. humeralis</taxonomicName>
as possibly polyphyletic, with partsister to a clade including G. atra, G. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFB76A08FB2197051D40BA96" authorityName="J. A. Allen" authorityYear="1917" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glauconycteris" isUncertain="true" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="76" pageNumber="834" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="humeralis">cf. humeralis</taxonomicName>
, and G. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFB76A08FC4A97D21A36BA96" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1901" box="[950,1078,395,420]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glauconycteris" isUncertain="true" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="76" pageNumber="834" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="beatrix">cf. beatrix</taxonomicName>
. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFB76A08FCEE97F21A47B928" pageId="76" pageNumber="834" type="distribution">
<caption id="90EB6676FFB76A08FCEE97F21A47B928" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6398093" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6398093" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6398093/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="76" pageNumber="834" targetBox="[171,763,280,695]" targetPageId="76">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFB76A08FCEE97F21A47B928" blockId="76.[786,1379,269,695]" pageId="76" pageNumber="834">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFFB76A08FCEE97F21DC2BAFE" bold="true" box="[786,962,427,460]" pageId="76" pageNumber="834">Distribution.</emphasis>
Confirmed records from 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFFB76A08FCEF978F1DB6BAC1" box="[787,950,470,499]" name="Democratic Republic of the Congo" pageId="76" pageNumber="834">DR Congo</collectingCountry>
